EN: We can't talk like chicken and duck, we need to insist on communicating in the right way.

ZH: 鸡同鸭讲只会导致误解的产生，真正理解对方才是关键。
EN: Talking like chicken and duck will only lead to misunderstandings. Truly understanding each other is the key.

